Author: metalbabble
Title: [ANN][EXY] Experty.io - Get Paid Calls For Your Expertise 📱
Body: How can you trust a team that raised 6500 ETH at 45-60% bonus both during and AFTER their crowdsale?  They were dishonest about their mcap, and they hid their smart contract by using a 3rd party payment processor.  The average bonus for their ICO was close to 50%. They made it sound like an exclusive rate was 20-30%. Candid questions were deflected. They completely screwed their investors because they wanted as much money as possible.  Experty is a joke in all investment circles, and a case study of what to watch out for with scammy ICOs.

Author: metalbabble
Title: [ANN][EXY] Experty.io - Get Paid Calls For Your Expertise 📱
Body: People make it sound like the price is a victim of the bear market or fud, or people just don't understand what a hidden gem this is.  The price is exactly where it deserves to be. The team squeezed all the value out of this for themselves and left the withered husk to die. They knew exactly what they were doing. They capitalized on free marketing, then gave their marketers the worst deal possible. They did back room deals with pools and gave 60% bonus. They sacrificed value to ensure their market cap was hit.  The result is what happens when you practically give your tokens away for free in order to cross the finish line. You get a worthless currency.

Author: krypto-joop
Title: [ANN][EXY] Experty.io - Get Paid Calls For Your Expertise 📱
Body: so what is it now, the total amount of tokens? 26million? 79million??  It was NOT clearly stated at all, maybe only buried somewhere in the whitepaper? Very deceiving how those seed tokens were slipped in. If known at the onset, I wouldn't have invested because it totally changed the token economics. Also, get someone senior for marketing & pr on the team. You have kind of a community crisis (judging from Telegram) right now, and it needs to be handled professionally, not by that colleague from Greece who has a condescending tone, e.g. by stating that "we wouldn't understand the marketing plan due to its detail" or similar. WTF he thinks he is? Having only dumbos in the Telegram who were kind enough to shill out a few grand for the ICO and should STFU otherwise? Many of the guys there are more experienced and have steeper careers / success whichever way you define it than the team.  Great product, that didn't change. Deceiving thing with the seed investor tokens, which will now lead me to offload my tokens at a considerable loss (second reason being that my email was leaked in the hacker attack, together with other personal details).  Nonetheless I hope the team learns from all these major hiccups during and post-ICO. I also recommend to get a leadership coach for leadership of the company. A guy like that will help you in a mini-crisis like you have now. Check that https://www.noomii.com to find one. And get a solid PR / Marketing guy to turn the tide around!!!

Author: rajatjain
Title: [ANN][EXY] Experty.io - Get Paid Calls For Your Expertise 📱
Body: If only everyone thought like this ! Every person expects more exchanges and more partnerships within a week and then they want the price to go 10x as soon as such news comes out and then they want to sell off those tokens and after making profit they expect the price to dip 90 percent so they can buy it cheaper again and then again expecting it to go 10x so they can sell off again. The thought process remains the same for everybody and when it doesn't happens, it makes some people frustrated. Market maturity is still a long way to go, we are seeing those traders enter crypto which never invested in the traditional markets and thus don't have an ounce of patience in them because they never experienced the good things that come of patience. The average age of a crypto trader is somewhat in 25 to 30 which is way too young for gaining the patience required to make money like warren buffet or any seasoned billionaire investor.

Author: rajatjain
Title: [ANN][EXY] Experty.io - Get Paid Calls For Your Expertise 📱
Body: Healthcare is a tricky business, there is a lot of regulations by countries as to if people can provide healthcare services to different country members. To some extent, i believe yes! services such as advices, checkups through video sharing and maybe general knowledge seekers can be given through experty but when compared to the full services of a specialist or a doctor which generally requires physical examination or laboratory tests might be difficult. There can be some issues with wrong service provided as well which again can be difficult to manage through experty. The legal framework is different in different countries and assuming the user base will be mostly from american and european countries whereas the service providers might be from asian countries, there can be a bit of a issue.

Author: ajolsson
Title: [ANN][EXY] Experty.io - Get Paid Calls For Your Expertise 📱
Body: This could be a game-changer for phone based advisory services. Applications like Skype played a pivotal role in off-shoring and thus reducing the expenses of call-centres for example. The problems with these is that they still rely on too much centralisation, and with companies like Skype now having been taken over by Microsoft, meaning even more of the profits were being captured by the owners. I REALLY like the idea of phone based information services providers, the greater efficiency of using each phone to operate as nodes in a peer to peer network, an the empowering and incentivising of participants through having a greater say and enjoying a greater share of the profits. I first encountered This is actually one of the first use-cases I have seen for blockchain tech that is scalable using current technology. And to be honest I would like to be part of it as a developer if the opportunity arises - I am legally trained and currently learning solidity - so please feel free to PM if you wold like to discuss this further.

Author: Experty
Title: [ANN][EXY] Experty.io - Get Paid Calls For Your Expertise 📱
Body: Hello Everyone,  Important update:  """With all of these changes, we want to give participants more time to participate in Proof of Caring. That’s why we are extending Proof of Caring until January 15th, 2018."""  More details at: https://medium.com/@experty_io/experty-sets-hardcap-at-9m-announces-proof-of-care-additions-b040264698cf    Or copy/paste of the article below:   EXPERTY SETS HARDCAP AT $9m ; ANNOUNCES PROOF OF CARE ADDITIONS  Due to the recent fluctuations in the value of Ethereum, we have decided to set a USD hard cap of $9M to compliment our original 33k ETH hard cap. If either the USD cap of $9m or the ETH cap of 33k are met, the sale will conclude and Experty will burn all remaining unsold tokens. Even better, we will burn all tokens proportionally, including team, founders, advisors, etc.    Please also read this announcement about Proof-of-Caring: https://medium.com/@experty_io/experty-pre-ico-rewarding-those-who-care-c0019f671b07   We have been listening to our community’s suggestions on how we can make Proof of Caring better, and we have come up with some exciting improvements. Some of the Proof of Caring contributors have gone so far above and beyond that we created a special tier, the Partner Tier, to reward them for their efforts.This tier is above Tier 1, and yields a bonus of 60%.  In addition, Tier 3 will now be able to participate in the pre-ICO with a bonus of 10%, and will be given to anyone who submits their Proof of Caring. This means that more people will be able to participate in the Experty pre-ICO.  Here is the breakdown for our new Proof of Caring system:  Partner Tier — 60% bonus + 5000 EXY (regardless of the contribution amount) + first access to testnet Experty app  Tier 1–40% + 1000 EXY (regardless of the contribution amount)  Tier 2–20%  Tier 3–10%  Tier 4 — Whitelisting for the ICO  With all of these changes, we want to give participants more time to participate in Proof of Caring. That’s why we are extending Proof of Caring until January 15th, 2018.  Here are some examples of outstanding Proof of Caring:  Example from Thailand  We have major PoC support from Thailand due to a supporter sharing Experty with one of the largest crypto communities there. In addition, this person wrote an article about Experty on a very popular Thailand crypto forum. Because of this supporter, we have many more people from Thailand sharing the word and talking about Experty.   https://www.facebook.com/groups/bitcointhaiclub/ https://www.facebook.com/whatthecoin/posts/306705549826106  https://ctc.in.th/index.php?r=blog-post%2Fview&id=37  https://medium.com/@pongpunpundech/experty-io-ico-blockchain-based-human-knowledge-exchange-c4953e57955c  Example from Spain  One of our supporters from Spain made a major contribution. They prepared a special presentation and shared information about Experty to their community on FB and in their newsletter.   Example from Japan  Experty has rapidly been gaining traction in Japan. Two people contacted us on Telegram and offered PoC by creating a JPY telegram about Experty. They have already invited almost 50 people to this telegram chat. They have an active discussion to support the education about PoC for people in Japan. Experty has received an incredibly positive response there, which can be seen by the many Japanese supporters that have been retweeting us on Twitter. We appreciate the dedication and hard work the two of them have put in to create awareness about Experty in Japan.   Example from Singapore  Shashwat is one of our most active supporters on telegram. He has already helped Experty by introducing us to many other potential partners. He has also demonstrated tremendous support for the project and has given us a lot of direct feedback. He is a great example of how being active in the community can provide a lot of value to the project. He also prepared an advertisement like video about Experty: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JzX-_l2CuqI  — — — — — — — —  These aren’t the only changes we’re rolling out. We have decided to wait until January to begin the ICO, mainly because we want to wait until the product is live before actually running the ICO. This will help us avoid any issues that arise from a legal standpoint, as any ICO (even utility tokens) which happen before a product release are viewed as a security by the SEC in the United States. We want to avoid this problem and focus on delivering, rather than just selling dreams in a whitepaper. Experty also has several exciting partnerships to announce between now and January, which will bring even more attention to the project.  The Experty team will be active on Telegram to answer any questions about these improvements, and to hear further suggestions.

People across the globe will be able to connect with others in a way that will encourage commerce.  3) SECURITY: Refunds and protection are provided to both parties via the smart contract. No 3rd party payment processor is required. Private keys are owned by the users.   Why is the Experty (EXY) token necessary?  1) FLEXIBILITY: If the Experty application reaches mass adoption it is possible that the Ethereum network will not scale quickly enough to handle all of our transactions. Having our own token (EXY) will allow us the flexibility to migrate to whichever platform is most suitable for our needs.  2) INCENTIVE:  We have tokens set aside for the purpose of incentivizing early adopters and influencers to use the Experty application. Our go-to-market strategy is to work closely with crypto influencers in the first year in order to optimize the user experience and interface. Once the Experty application is ready for mass market we will target mass market influencers/celebrities such as Christiano Ronaldo, Madonna, and Justin Bieber to help bring Experty into the mainstream.  3) PREMIUM FUNCTIONALITIES: Instead of paying for premium memberships, users who have a certain amount of EXY staked in their wallet will be able to use premium features without additional fees. Examples of premium features include: - Paid group calls (ie. webinars) - Conversation recording - Advanced scheduling - Paid group chats like in Telegram

Author: kriptomaniac
Title: [ANN][EXY] Experty.io - Get Paid Calls For Your Expertise 📱
Body: I have some personal experience about offering distance consulting and, in fact, I have charged for it. According to my own experience, if you want to offer your distance advice now you have these options:  One is to hire an additional rate telephone, which has the advantage that the payment method is automatic (depending on the number of minutes the call lasted) but it has the following disadvantages:  1.- The telephone company takes a large percentage of your income, which means lower income for the professional advisor and higher expense for the consultant.  2.- It only works to answer calls in your own country.  Another option is to perform professional advice through services such as Skype. It has the advantage that counseling can be extended to everyone, but it has the following disadvantage:  1.- You have to previously agree with the person you are going to attend at what time the connection will be made.  2.- The payment of the advising has to be done before the videoconference, it is necessary to give an account number, make the payment and, if it is an international transfer, that can suppose delays of 2 or 3 days until the transfer is verified. This of course is not operative when the advice is done through the Internet precisely because of the urgency of obtaining the response from an expert.  Considering the problems that I have encountered in online counseling, I think Experty.io can offer some solution to these problems. Experty.io is built on the blockchain that, by itself, is specially indicated for micropayments, eliminates intermediaries and makes payments secure and fast.  In addition, Experty.io solves the problem of automated payment by minutes to which applications such as Skype do not solve.  And an other advantage: highly qualified professionals from countries where salaries are very low may offer their services to other parts of the world where salaries are higher, which will be a good opportunity for these professionals.

Author: Experty
Title: [ANN][EXY] Experty.io - Get Paid Calls For Your Expertise 📱
Body: 1) It's not a marketplace. it's a paid calling app where influencers put their calling link on their profile. You pay people based on their online presence.  2) Every expert will have refunds rules, if you call him and you are not happy you will be able to get a refund  3) There will be review and rating mechanism, but the final decision if you want to call an expert is to the caller.  EXPERTY IS NOT A MARKETPLACE To build a fully decentralized platform we decided to depart from the classic approach of creating our own Marketplace where users can search for a specialist. The current market is already supersaturated with services in which knowledge seekers can easily find Experts - who are already verified.  Instead of having a centralized marketplace, we are implementing a totally decentralized solution. Users will be able to share their Experty.io contact information wherever they’d like, such as discussion boards, LinkedIn profiles, Facebook profiles, on their websites, Twitter, etc. while Experty.io app will be responsible for knowledge for money exchange.  This approach allows us to omit two huge problems:  Identity of the Experts, which is already verified by third party services. Lack of potential customers, because of a large amount of users in already existing services.

Author: cwarloe
Title: [ANN][EXY] Experty.io - Get Paid Calls For Your Expertise 📱
Body: Wow. I don't think I have a single negative thing to say about this project - which is a huge compliment, since I have looked a well over 100 ICOs this summer and fall! First and foremost, following the very concept of crypto, it does NOT rely on altruism in any way. Those who have expertise are paid for their time and wisdom, and again, because it uses smart contracts, no one has to trust anyone else's ability to pay. And sounds like you will have a minimally functional product available by the end of the fall. Seems like you have set up some great partnerships as well. You guys have even bothered to sync up with Quantstamp, another ICO that I am pretty sold on, to do testing and validation. It's all there - this is what ICOs should be for! Needless to say, I am sold...  I will be following on Twitter joining the Telegram group to ask and read answers to questions, and ultimately, I plan on investing in this ICO myself. I think there is an airdrop as part of bitcointalk, which I definitely want to be a part of, and if there is a bounty campaign (I haven't gotten that far into the bitcointalk posts yet) I will be participating in those as well. I think this ICO just vaulted into my Top 5 ICOs of the fall!  And, as I was writing this, I just realized I might have some expertise to offer, and I am sure there are a lot of other average joes out there who do as well. And in fact, I will probably also be willing to pay for advice, so my investment in tokens (and any payments I might get) could even be used to pay for service, so this really is a utility token and not just a security which is just pretending to be a token! Looking forward to the progress of this project.

Author: vezpit
Title: [ANN][EXY] Experty.io - Get Paid Calls For Your Expertise 📱
Body: Interesting project.  There are a few points which come to mind.  Seen this type of business on the web & think that there is one major point in that the 'expert' appointed must be a true 'expert' in the field .  For example, a Lawyer asked a technical issue of law in the Country you reside in must be able to fully understand your question & the 'background ' of the question.   It is very difficult to satisfy someone via a short 'conversation' or text if the subset of the question is not in the area of expertize.  A second point is how can you be satisfied with your 'experts' unless there is a considerable amount of vetting & monitoring.  All this takes time & who pays for that time.  A busy 'expert' in their own profession would not be interested, yet the is the type of person you want.  Someone with time on their hands may not be a worthwhile expert.

Title: [ANN][EXY] Experty.io - Get Paid Calls For Your Expertise 📱
Body: Thanks for your feedback.  Check the main post about WHT do EXY tokens:  Why is the Experty (EXY) token necessary?  1) FLEXIBILITY: If the Experty application reaches mass adoption it is possible that the Ethereum network will not scale quickly enough to handle all of our transactions. Having our own token (EXY) will allow us the flexibility to migrate to whichever platform is most suitable for our needs.  2) INCENTIVE:  We have tokens set aside for the purpose of incentivizing early adopters and influencers to use the Experty application. Our go-to-market strategy is to work closely with crypto influencers in the first year in order to optimize the user experience and interface. Once the Experty application is ready for mass market we will target mass market influencers/celebrities such as Christiano Ronaldo, Madonna, and Justin Bieber to help bring Experty into the mainstream.  3) PREMIUM FUNCTIONALITIES: Instead of paying for premium memberships, users who have a certain amount of EXY staked in their wallet will be able to use premium features without additional fees. Examples of premium features include: - Paid group calls (ie. webinars) - Conversation recording - Advanced scheduling - Paid group chats like in Telegram

Author: tyKiwanuka
Title: [ANN][EXY] Experty.io - Get Paid Calls For Your Expertise 📱
Body: The presentation of your project is very professional. Good website, the explainer video is great, big team, very responsive.  But I have my doubts, if this will work or at least work the way you want it to work. Nowadays people always want to get everything for free. In the times of Internet, it’s very easy to get information for free. In special or unique cases (e.g. legal or medical advice), where it’s hard to get free information/advice over the internet, I doubt that people would use your paid calls, but rather consult someone, who they can talk to in a personal meeting – but maybe I am too old school.  That would leave you in a small corridor between free information provided via the internet and special cases, where there is a need to do consulting by meeting someone in person.

Author: gargusio
Title: [ANN][EXY] Experty.io - Get Paid Calls For Your Expertise 📱
Body: It all looks very interesting, but I am wondering how you are going to solve the issue of different pay expectations around the globe. For example, a medical expert in Canada will want to be paid much more than his equivalent, let's say, in Venezuela. Won't that reduce the number of experts?  Also how would all "experts" be checked to be the ones they claim to be?  It seems like a very good idea but might be hard to implement on a global scale. It might succeed on local markets though, same as Gumtree did.  I'm waiting to hear from you and all I can say is "powodzenia chlopaki"

Author: Mattsac
Title: [ANN][EXY] Experty.io - Get Paid Calls For Your Expertise 📱
Body: Firstly to create fully decentralized platform we decided to depart from the classic approach of creating our own Marketplace where users can search for a specialist. The current market is already supersaturated with services in which knowledge seekers can easily find Experts - who are already verified. We want to integrate with this kind of services, so you will know if expert you want to consult with is worth calling.  Secondly, yes we are going to implement reputation system, so you will be able to rate expert after consultation.

Author: Mattsac
Title: [ANN][EXY] Experty.io - Get Paid Calls For Your Expertise 📱
Body: Our goal is to create product available for everyone(crypto and non-crypto users) , If you check our roadmap you can see that we are planning to implement FIAT gateway, in another words we are planning to enter mass-market with Experty app. https://www.experty.io/img/mct-graphics/en/roadmap.png  If we are talking about promotion: We want to market Experty on few fields. Firstly we want to create traction in crypto space due to cooperation with influencers, YouTuber's, well-known crypto firms etc. that will promote and use Experty app. To reach crypto and non-crypto individual users we want to cooperate with well known experts, celebrities, influencers etc. that have huge audience to use our app. To this purpose we have tokens reserved for partners that will incentivize them to use Experty. If we are talking about groups of users our approach is to cooperate with large portals that already have huge users(experts) data base. We want to integrate Experty inside their websites. This approach creates win-win situation - they are creating additional source of income thanks to Experty, while in the same time we generate users for our app.

Author: Mattsac
Title: [ANN][EXY] Experty.io - Get Paid Calls For Your Expertise 📱
Body: We want to market Experty on few fields. Firstly we want to create traction in crypto space due to cooperation with influencers, YouTuber's, well-known crypto firms etc. that will promote and use Experty app. To reach crypto and non-crypto individual users we want to cooperate with well known experts, celebrities, influencers etc. that have huge audience to use our app. To this purpose we have tokens reserved for partners that will incentivize them to use Experty. If we are talking about groups our approach is to cooperate with large portals that already have huge users(experts) data base. We want to integrate Experty inside their websites. This approach creates win-win situation - they are creating additional source of income thanks to Experty, while in the same time we generate users for our app.

So yes, I think this could really gain traction in the coming months, if properly conducted.  A 3-year timeframe seems reasonable, but things in blockchain space are really moving too fast. If they can differentiate from these existing services, this could easily go off the ground.

Author: cherrymonsoon
Title: [ANN][EXY] Experty.io - Get Paid Calls For Your Expertise 📱
Body: Finally there is a new revolutionary way to exchange knowledge over the internet in a much more efficient way than other methods. People who seek knowledge online no longer have to transfer funds before receiving advice from an expert. Therefore this reduces/eliminates the risk of unpredictable consultation time and costs. Secondly, the experts who provide the people seeking advice/knowledge no longer have to wait several days for receiving payment and most importantly he/she does not have to stress and wonder if he/she will ever get paid for the advice/knowledge that they just shared. Experty provides a decentralized calling platform on the blockchain. I am excited about this wonderful solution because it addresses key real world applications such a medical consulting (especially in rural areas) and much more. Please go check out https://www.experty.io and click on the Live Demo link, it is absolutely amazing. It truly is a WIN-WIN situation for both knowledge seekers and knowledge providers.

Author: gkucmierz
Title: [ANN][EXY] Experty.io - Get Paid Calls For Your Expertise 📱
Body: This is why we have EXY tokens, it was written in the first ANN post:  Why is the Experty (EXY) token necessary?  1) FLEXIBILITY: If the Experty application reaches mass adoption it is possible that the Ethereum network will not scale quickly enough to handle all of our transactions. Having our own token (EXY) will allow us the flexibility to migrate to whichever platform is most suitable for our needs.  2) INCENTIVE:  We have tokens set aside for the purpose of incentivizing early adopters and influencers to use the Experty application. Our go-to-market strategy is to work closely with crypto influencers in the first year in order to optimize the user experience and interface. Once the Experty application is ready for mass market we will target mass market influencers/celebrities such as Christiano Ronaldo, Madonna, and Justin Bieber to help bring Experty into the mainstream.  3) PREMIUM FUNCTIONALITIES: Instead of paying for premium memberships, users who have a certain amount of EXY staked in their wallet will be able to use premium features without additional fees. Examples of premium features include: - Paid group calls (ie. webinars) - Conversation recording - Advanced scheduling - Paid group chats like in Telegram

Also we don't create marketplace on which you will be able to search for an expert. Our approach is to create a tool - Experty app will be working like Skype/Whatsapp ID or regular phone number that you can share with anyone, the difference is you will get paid for your time. Author: Experty
Title: [ANN][EXY] Experty.io - Get Paid Calls For Your Expertise 📱
Body: Thanks for the question. Everything is explained in the first post, let me copy past it here:  ABOUT BLOCKCHAIN AND EXY TOKENS Why is Experty better with BLOCKCHAIN?  1) BUSINESS EXECUTION: We don't hold users’ private keys, so there are less legal issues for us to work through.  2) A NEW ECONOMY: Experts from countries such as Venezuela (eg. spanish teachers) will have access to a new tool enabling monetization of their time on the global market. This has never been possible before Experty. People across the globe will be able to connect with others in a way that will encourage commerce.  3) SECURITY: Refunds and protection are provided to both parties via the smart contract. No 3rd party payment processor is required. Private keys are owned by the users.   Why is the Experty (EXY) token necessary?  1) FLEXIBILITY: If the Experty application reaches mass adoption it is possible that the Ethereum network will not scale quickly enough to handle all of our transactions. Having our own token (EXY) will allow us the flexibility to migrate to whichever platform is most suitable for our needs.  2) INCENTIVE:  We have tokens set aside for the purpose of incentivizing early adopters and influencers to use the Experty application. Our go-to-market strategy is to work closely with crypto influencers in the first year in order to optimize the user experience and interface. Once the Experty application is ready for mass market we will target mass market influencers/celebrities such as Christiano Ronaldo, Madonna, and Justin Bieber to help bring Experty into the mainstream.  3) PREMIUM FUNCTIONALITIES: Instead of paying for premium memberships, users who have a certain amount of EXY staked in their wallet will be able to use premium features without additional fees. Examples of premium features include: - Paid group calls (ie. webinars) - Conversation recording - Advanced scheduling - Paid group chats like in Telegram    Does it answer your question?

Title: [ANN][EXY] Experty.io - Get Paid Calls For Your Expertise 📱
Body: There has been many new coins lately with a ton of airdrops and launch campaigns coming through this forum. I have been very reluctant to follow these launches due to the lack of professionalism, creative and innovation surrounding their projects. I have found only a couple projects worth watching and this happens to be one of them. The website, forum post here, and social media campaigns, are enough to show anyone that this team is serious about innovation and they are going to make a significant impact.  The one piece of advice I want to offer is to possibly add a short video on the homepage of the website which explains in a very simple manner exactly what this project is aiming to accomplish and how they intent on doing that. By doing this you will greatly improve your chance of getting people that land on the site to convert to believers. Not everyone is technically savvy, but that doesn't mean they don't want to invest in your ideas and vision.  For example, put the video that you posted in this thread (https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aJoDr6ax5gI) on the homepage of the website.  I joined the telegram channel and followed you on Twitter so I can stay up-to-date on the project. Best of luck and it's nice to see such a well put together launch.
